highlights.text: Disney has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “I Always Wanted A Brother” is the highest at #1.
“Bye Bye” by Folake, Mads Mikkelsen, Joanna Jones, and Disney is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #3.
“Sailor Song” by Gigi Perez has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 145 days straight.
“İçim Yanar” by Ferdi Tayfur is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 8 spots at #11.
